<title>SOUTH AFRICA: Towles Edgar Jacobs says in talks.</title>
<headline>Towles Edgar Jacobs says in talks.</headline>
<dateline>JOHANNESBURG 1997-05-08</dateline>
<text>
<p>Towles, Edgar Jacobs Ltd, a clothing manufacturer, said on Thursday it was currently in talks which could affect the company's share price.</p>
<p>The company said in a cautionary annoucement that shareholders should exercise caution in their share dealings until further notice.</p>
<p>-- Johannesburg newsroom, +27-11 482 1003</p>
